<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>

<section xml:id="Slope" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  <title>The Slope of a Line</title>
    <p>
        In this section, we will define the slope of a line and learn how to calculate it.
    </p>

    <definition xml:id="slope-definition">
        <statement>
            <p>
                The <term>slope</term> of a line is a measure of its steepness, defined as the ratio of the change in <term>y</term> to the change in <term>x</term>.
            </p>
        </statement>
    </definition>

    </section>